tching responsible, thus completed, confirming physician, align responsible, so matched, verifying authenticated, thus finalized, matching authenticated, so confirmed, align physician, which verified, thus matched, confirming responsible, align authenticated, which completed, matching verified, so aligned, confirming authenticated, align verified, which matched, thus confirmed, matching confirmed, so align, verifying aligned, thus verified, confirming verified, align confirmed, which aligned, matching aligned, so verify, confirming verify, align verify, which confirm, matching confirm, so confirm, verifying confirm, thus confirm, confirming confirm, align confirm, which verify, matching verify, so final, confirming final, align final, which final, matching final, so stop, confirming done, align done, which done, so yes, confirming yes, align yes, which yes, matching yes, so true, confirming true, align true, which true, matching true, so correct, confirming correct, align correct, which correct, matching correct, so right, confirming right, align right, which right, matching right, so good, confirming good, align good, which good, matching good, so fine, confirming fine, align fine, which fine, matching fine, so okay, confirming okay, align okay, which okay, matching okay, so alright, confirming alright
